17641480330_2157\"><span id=\"m_200198629313880101gmail-yui_3_17_2_1_1617641480330_2158\">Lab&nbsp;Evaluation&nbsp;will be taken by your respective&nbsp;lab&nbsp;faculties in your pre-decided slots.</span></li><li id=\"m_200198629313880101gmail-yui_3_17_2_1_1617641480330_2157\"><span>It is also mandatory to submit the Lab files of 8085, 8086 and Interfacing (soft copy) to your respective Lab teachers.&nbsp;</span></li></ol><div><br></div></div><br><p></p></div>","visible":1,"uservisible":true,"visibleoncoursepage":1,"modicon":"https://lms.thapar.edu/moodle/theme/image.php/moove/page/1659956381/icon","modname":"page","modplural":"Pages","indent":0,"onclick":"","afterlink":null,"customdata":"\"\"","noviewlink":false,"completion":1,"completiondata":{"state":0,"timecompleted":0,"overrideby":null,"valueused":false},"contents":[{"type":"file","filename":"index.html","filepath":"/","filesize":0,"fileurl":"https://lms.thapar.edu/moodle/webservice/pluginfile.php/580984/mod_page/content/index.html?forcedownload=1","timecreated":null,"timemodified":1774334465,"sortorder":1,"userid":null,"author":null,"license":null}],"contentsinfo":{"filescount":1,"filessize":0,"lastmodified":1774334465,"mimetypes":[],"repositorytype":""}},{"id":158865,"url":"https://lms.thapar.edu/moodle/mod/page/view.php?id=158865","name":"Theory Quiz-1 (Marks: 10), Lab Quiz-1 (Marks: 5)","instance":4267,"contextid":580986,"visible":1,"uservisible":true,"visibleoncoursepage":1,"modicon":"https://lms.thapar.edu/moodle/theme/image.php/moove/page/1659956381/icon","modname":"page","modplural":"Pages","indent":0,"onclick":"","afterlink":null,"customdata":"\"\"","noviewlink":false,"completion":1,"completiondata":{"state":0,"timecompleted":0,"overrideby":null,"valueused":false},"contents":[{"type":"file","filename":"Theory Quiz-1_Seating Plan (UCS617).pdf","filepath":"/","filesize":69211,"fileurl":"https://lms.thapar.edu/moodle/webservice/pluginfile.php/580986/mod_page/content/45/Theory%20Quiz-1_Seating%20Plan%20%2